  #welcome.section
    h3 Welcome
    p
      | Bible Community Church is a body of believers dedicated to serving and worshipping 
      | the one true God. BCC believes the Bible is the infallible and inerrant Word of
      | God and that the Bible is sufficient in providing truth concerning salvation and
      | living a life glorifying to the Lord Jesus Christ. As a church,
      | we live to spread the good news of Jesus Christ to sinners everywhere
      | so that they may receive salvation from God's wrath.

